Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.12,0:00:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,At a certain hot spring, there is an inn where liars gather
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.12,0:00:10.40,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.16,0:00:11.32,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Why are you so angry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:15.32,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,No no, it's not that I'm mad
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:18.88,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I forgot how this thing started
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.60,0:00:23.00,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,If we started right away or not
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.44,0:00:23.28,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Ah I see
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.72,0:00:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Fully Improvised Liar's Inn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.40,0:00:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The person on the card nominates someone to tell a lie
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.44,0:00:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The nominated person must maintain the lie given to them
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:39.36,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Here I go
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.36,0:00:41.12,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yeah go on
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.12,0:00:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hosei nominates someone to tell a lie
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.08,0:00:50.76,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I think it was during the student years, so this is a decades old story,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.16,0:00:57.48,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto-san, you went to a vocational school for Onmiyoji right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.16,0:00:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,270.474)}TN: Onmiyoji are people that study Onmyodo; "a system of natural science, astronomy, almanac, divination and magic"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.36,0:00:57.48,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I did. In fact I still go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.76,0:00:59.08,Hosei,,0,0,0,,To the Onmiyoji?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:01:02.24,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I don't really know anything about it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.24,0:01:04.00,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Can anyone go to the classes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:11.72,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Ah, this is something that's kind of bad to say, I had a rewards points card,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.72,0:01:15.64,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,And if you got enough points, you could get into that sort of thing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.64,0:01:18.68,Endo,,0,0,0,,Eh, you can get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:20.56,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I think Hamada can get it too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.56,0:01:21.60,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.60,0:01:28.68,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's in the top ten. There's a special catalog for long time customers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.68,0:01:30.92,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah there's lots of stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:32.12,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You can stay in a hotel somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.28,0:01:33.44,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Stuff like that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:34.60,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Special prizes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.72,0:01:38.60,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Special prizes and so on. But on the back, is the real thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.60,0:01:42.07,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I didn't know about that at all
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.60,0:01:42.68,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,"You may be able to enter Onmiyoji!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.48,0:01:42.68,Hamada,,0,0,0,,"May be"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.68,0:01:47.80,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That's on purpose, like "You might". You can go actually of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.80,0:01:52.40,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,But on purpose, to catch your attention. Like "You might!".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.68,0:01:59.76,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,So it's been, 2, 3, ... 20 years? 20 years I've been doing this Onmiyoji thing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.24,0:02:01.76,Hosei,,0,0,0,,How many points does it cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:04.72,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That one, it costs 58,000
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:06.36,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It costs 58,000 points
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.64,0:02:08.20,Endo,,0,0,0,,That's quite a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:13.56,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Most people, most people spend it on Matsuzaka Beef
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.56,0:02:17.64,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,If they had that many points? It is quite a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:19.76,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Excuse me but,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.76,0:02:24.64,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,At this age, marbled beef is very heavy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.92,0:02:33.88,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,When you're younger though, you can eat 200-300 grams easily
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:38.32,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Enough of that. Are you knowledgeable about it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:41.04,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Of course I am, I've been doing it for 20 years
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.04,0:02:43.21,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.21,0:02:45.34,Hosei,,0,0,0,,What is Onmiyoji?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.34,0:02:50.56,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Ghost expulsion, and also ghost capture- chewing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:51.92,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Chewing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.92,0:02:53.28,Hosei,,0,0,0,,You eat ghosts?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.28,0:02:55.40,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I have to chew them, the small ones
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.60,0:02:58.36,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It puts people off though so I didn't wanna talk about this
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:00.44,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I didn't know about this
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:03.24,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna say too much
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:04.60,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Please tell us (x2)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:06.44,Hamada,,0,0,0,,How do you capture them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.44,0:03:08.40,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,There's different types of ghosts too
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:14.96,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,So, if I had to explain it, like a Japanese version of Ghostbusters,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:16.44,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That's easy to explain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.44,0:03:18.36,Hamada,,0,0,0,,They use like machines and stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:22.56,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You know that start shaped thing? What do you call it, the star thing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:25.56,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I summon them there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.56,0:03:27.96,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,By like placing a Banana or something
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.96,0:03:29.24,Endo,,0,0,0,,Banana?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.24,0:03:32.08,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,When I wake up in the morning I catch quite a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.08,0:03:34.76,Endo,,0,0,0,,It's like you're capturing insects isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.76,0:03:36.80,Hosei,,0,0,0,,You use a Banana?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:39.96,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What do you do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.96,0:03:43.48,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It depends, on my mood, if I'm hungry I'll chew them
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.48,0:03:44.84,Hamada,,0,0,0,,So you are eating them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:47.28,Endo,,0,0,0,,You just eat them like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:50.12,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You feel the electric shock though,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.80,0:03:50.52,Endo,,0,0,0,,Electric shock?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:53.68,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Cause there's a thing (barrier) there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:53.68,Hamada,,0,0,0,,You're the one who put it there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:04:01.92,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Ah, right, I have to break the seal, and then eat them
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:03.40,Hosei,,0,0,0,,How do you break it, like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.40,0:04:06.68,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Like "I'm gon-na break the seal"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:09.76,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I don't have my notes right now though
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.76,0:04:11.48,Hamada,,0,0,0,,You look at your notes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:13.08,Endo,,0,0,0,,Even though it's been 20 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:20.12,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You can't memorise it! I'll show it to you then, it's super thick
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:23.00,Hamada,,0,0,0,,You basically just eat them? Are there big ones too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:24.24,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,There are big ones
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:26.92,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What do you do for those ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:27.32,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(738,901)}How large are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.32,0:04:29.12,Hosei,,0,0,0,,The biggest one
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:31.64,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Hmm, I guess about this big
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.64,0:04:33.44,Hamada,,0,0,0,,That's not big
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.44,0:04:35.60,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You guys don't understand the category!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:41.28,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You don't know! This is huge, the normal ones are this small
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.28,0:04:44.52,Endo,,0,0,0,,Ah, normally they're this size?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.52,0:04:46.68,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Ghosts are like that? I thought they were bigger
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:48.12,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:52.44,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You've never seen a ghost before in your lives and yet you're deciding what's big and small
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.44,0:04:56.56,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Saying things like "that's small!" pisses me off \N I'm done! I'm not talking anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.60,0:04:58.68,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I'm done talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:05:04.72,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Please don't say that. We just don't know anything, I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:07.88,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Is it just ghosts around you or do people call you over?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.88,0:05:09.68,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,They do they do
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.68,0:05:15.24,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,There's a lot in the political world
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.64,0:05:18.36,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I'm only telling you guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.36,0:05:19.20,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What kind of ghosts?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:22.00,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Only I can see them, you guys can't right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:26.08,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,There was one climbing up and down the Diet building
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.08,0:05:28.12,Hamada,,0,0,0,,That's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.12,0:05:31.88,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Do you charge high fees for places like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.20,0:05:36.24,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I do say "It's not about the money"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.24,0:05:42.12,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,But even if I don't take their money, they send me impressive gifts at the end of the year
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:46.80,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Like Matsusaka Beef
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:47.16,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Matsusaka Beef?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.16,0:05:49.60,Hosei,,0,0,0,,It should be on the Point Card
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.60,0:05:52.60,Endo,,0,0,0,,You don't like Matsusaka Beef?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:56.32,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,No, no, I did the Onmiyoji because I don't like Matsusaka Beef,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.32,0:06:00.88,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,But in the end, I still received it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:03.08,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,In the end-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.08,0:06:11.09,Hamada,,0,0,0,,If we can't see them it doesn't matter
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.12,0:06:11.72,Hosei,,0,0,0,,You eat them though right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:12.96,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I do I do
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:14.88,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.88,0:06:17.34,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,One of them even ran away after I ate it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.44,0:06:17.64,Endo,,0,0,0,,That's scary
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:19.60,Endo,,0,0,0,,That's super scary
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:21.60,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,One leg, it ran away on one leg
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,0:06:21.72,Endo,,0,0,0,,Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.16,0:06:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Endo nominates someone to tell a lie
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:25.44,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Endo-kun
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.00,0:06:28.96,Endo,,0,0,0,,He came to Gaki the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.96,0:06:32.00,Endo,,0,0,0,,Ryuchell, you know him right
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.12,0:06:32.04,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ryuchell
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.04,0:06:36.60,Endo,,0,0,0,,Hosei-san, I've heard he's rather a close relative of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:39.08,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Oh, how?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:43.64,Endo,,0,0,0,,Yeah, are you relatives?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.64,0:06:47.00,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Would you call us relatives?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:53.60,Hosei,,0,0,0,,He's my father's sister's son
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:55.12,Endo,,0,0,0,,That's a relative
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:56.96,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's a relative
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:58.64,Endo,,0,0,0,,You're pretty closely related
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.92,0:07:01.76,Endo,,0,0,0,,You guys must meet if you're that closely related
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:07.04,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I've never met him before, but I do care for him
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:10.88,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Eh? But when he came the other day it didn't seem like that at all
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.88,0:07:14.32,Hosei,,0,0,0,,He did say that. I am a comedian,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:19.48,Hosei,,0,0,0,,And Ryuchell, is a fashion...person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:24.08,Hosei,,0,0,0,,So Comedians and Fashion cannot mix
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:28.04,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That's not true. You see it on variety shows all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:30.13,Hosei,,0,0,0,,It's impossible after all
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:30.76,Endo,,0,0,0,,Is it hard to work together?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.76,0:07:37.20,Hosei,,0,0,0,,It sure is...Cause sometimes I can tell he's looking at me, cause we're relatives
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.20,0:07:39.60,Endo,,0,0,0,,So you only met recently
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:41.92,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Did he contact you before he came to Gaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:44.52,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Actually he did
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:47.44,Hosei,,0,0,0,,On LINE, he said "Next time,"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:51.76,Hosei,,0,0,0,,He calls me Hosei-chan you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:56.96,Hosei,,0,0,0,,"Hosei-chan, I'm coming to Gaki, let's work together"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.96,0:07:59.84,Hosei,,0,0,0,,He said like "Please bully a little"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.84,0:08:01.96,Hosei,,0,0,0,,"Please bully a little" he said
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:03.28,Endo,,0,0,0,,Who bullies who?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:04.36,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Ryuchell,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.64,0:08:05.84,Hamada,,0,0,0,,He's bullied by who?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:07.00,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:11.28,Endo,,0,0,0,,Like "please pick on me" you mean? But that didn't happen
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:16.96,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I didn't do it of course, but he did say "Please bully me" in an Osaka dialect
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:17.40,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:19.00,Hosei,,0,0,0,,In Osaka-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:19.48,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\pos(724,890)}So hard to follow
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.08,0:08:21.92,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Is my story hard to follow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:24.84,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's hard to follow, it's super hard to follow
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.84,0:08:26.56,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Why that face...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:28.84,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Who picked the name Ryuchell
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.84,0:08:36.40,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Ryuchell...was decided by my mother's side
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.40,0:08:37.60,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's his real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:40.18,Hosei,,0,0,0,,It's his real name
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:40.68,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,That's his real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:43.32,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Ryuchell isn't his real name,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.32,0:08:46.68,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Ryuchie~.... Ryuichi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.68,0:08:48.56,Endo,,0,0,0,,Ryuichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:48.56,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ryuichi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.56,0:08:51.36,Endo,,0,0,0,,It's Ryuichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.40,0:08:51.36,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Ryuichi is his real name
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:54.56,Endo,,0,0,0,,So Ryuchell isn't his real name at all then. It's Ryuichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.56,0:08:55.44,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.44,0:08:57.44,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He said it was Ryuchell before\N{\rHamada}He did
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.44,0:09:03.00,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I messed up his real name, but I asked him for the truth and he said it's Ryuichi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.00,0:09:07.28,Hosei,,0,0,0,,He does a lot of secret work! He does it all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.56,0:09:10.24,Hosei,,0,0,0,,The beauty parlor and everything is done secretly
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:13.64,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.64,0:09:18.44,Endo,,0,0,0,,Like in real life him in and Peko aren't dating
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.44,0:09:24.00,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Oh sorry, Peko-chan and him are good friends
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.84,0:09:28.48,Endo,,0,0,0,,Oh I see
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:29.08,Hosei,,0,0,0,,It was dangerous at one point
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:35.08,Hosei,,0,0,0,,It was dangerous at one point, but my dad got involved, and I got involved, and we worked things out
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.08,0:09:36.00,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:38.00,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Oh you don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:42.04,Hosei,,0,0,0,,When was it again? Right back when Rachell...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:43.24,Endo,,0,0,0,,Rachell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.20,0:09:48.72,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Horrible. This guy sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.72,0:09:51.28,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,This guy really sucks
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.70,0:10:01.88,Credits,,0,0,0,,Timed & Typeset by: Kedomas\NTranslated by: senor_wristband
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:10:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Fully Improvised! Liar's Inn. They must maintain the lie no matter what!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.48,0:10:04.72,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Here I go
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.28,0:10:05.00,Endo,,0,0,0,,Go ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamada nominates someone to tell a lie
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:07.84,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Hamada-san
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:09.52,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Dahama-san
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.32,0:10:14.20,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Tanaka, earlier I saw you really fighting with your manager
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,0:10:19.12,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What happened? I've never seen you be that angry before
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.36,0:10:25.80,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Well, to sum it up, I couldn't take it anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:28.60,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Like I exploded
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:29.92,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Tanaka exploded...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.92,0:10:31.68,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.68,0:10:35.24,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,It's his mocking
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.24,0:10:37.20,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Him mocking me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:43.60,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Tanaka maybe you're overthinking it. A manager, making fun of their talent?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:47.92,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,First, he said he really hates me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:49.32,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,My manager
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.32,0:10:50.64,Endo,,0,0,0,,He said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.64,0:10:52.92,Hosei,,0,0,0,,That does kinda suck
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:54.36,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,It does, but he said it to me very clearly
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:10:56.10,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714,898)}Did you ask why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.16,0:10:57.48,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I did. He said "You're not funny"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:11:01.36,Endo,,0,0,0,,That's... I hate that too actually
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:04.16,Hosei,,0,0,0,,That's not good
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:10.08,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,He said he hates having to manage an unfunny comedian
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.08,0:11:12.36,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Why does he think you're unfunny?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:13.88,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,My performance
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.12,0:11:17.52,Hamada,,0,0,0,,He didn't say anything about Endo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.22,0:11:19.82,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714,896)}It seems he doesn't really like Endo
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.52,0:11:19.08,Endo,,0,0,0,,No way, me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.68,0:11:23.60,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Well yeah, unfortunately it does make sense
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:29.12,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,If he hates Tanaka, it makes sense he wouldn't really like Endo
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.24,0:11:31.54,Endo,,0,0,0,,I never really got that impression
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.68,0:11:34.44,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,It is unfortunate, but yeah he hates me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:36.92,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,And, yes, he hates Endo too
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:38.68,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Like joint responsibility kind of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.68,0:11:43.68,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,He said he hates me, which I don't like, \Nand even after this is over, I just hate it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:47.48,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Cause even after this he's gonna say it again\N "You weren't funny again today huh?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:51.92,Endo,,0,0,0,,That's really not alright
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:51.92,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,If someone says that to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:56.40,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Your mind just starts to snap. Every set, every shooting, no matter the occasion
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:58.44,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,So he said it to you before we started today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.44,0:12:00.40,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,He did he did
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:03.00,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,He said like "You're gonna be funny today, right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.00,0:12:05.32,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,So you just snapped
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:07.80,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I snapped like "Cut it out already, every single day you do this"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.80,0:12:09.36,Hamada,,0,0,0,,That's what I saw
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.36,0:12:11.80,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,That's what you saw, me telling him to cut it out
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:16.56,Hosei,,0,0,0,,So when you got the job on ZIP, it would be normal for a manager to say "Congrats, do your best!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:18.52,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,He didn't say that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:23.29,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,"What the hell are you gonna be able to do on ZIP" is what he said
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.36,0:12:22.96,Endo,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:25.12,Endo,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:26.12,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,And that just made me snap
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.12,0:12:28.80,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That would make you snap
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.80,0:12:32.44,Hosei,,0,0,0,,What was the first thing you yelled at him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.44,0:12:37.72,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,"Stop calling me like boring and unfunny"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.16,0:12:44.80,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,"Stop saying that to me, it's driving me crazy!" is what I said to him
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:49.68,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,And right after I said that he beat me up...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:53.80,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,And you don't remember
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:59.92,Hosei,,0,0,0,,He beat you so hard you forgot, that's the worst \N He called you unfunny and then beat you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:01.44,Hamada,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.72,0:13:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto nominates someone
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:04.60,Endo,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto-san again, you will pick someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:11.60,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I heard Nukumizu-san smacked Yamasaki in the toilet
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:13.04,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.88,0:13:17.36,Hamada,,0,0,0,, That guy is really mild mannered
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.36,0:13:20.48,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,In the NTV Kojimachi toilet, here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:28.48,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Yes yes yes.\N Right now, and I don't agree, but everyone says my hair is getting thinner right
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.48,0:13:30.38,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Ah your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:32.12,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Yeah, my hair is getting thinner
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.76,0:13:32.88,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I don't think it is though
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.88,0:13:39.88,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I get it thinned by the hairdresser. They take a lot off using the crescent moon scissors
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:46.28,Hosei,,0,0,0,,So I do tell people that when they ask me, not just Nukumizu-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:53.36,Hosei,,0,0,0,,At other studios when people say "Oh your hair is getting thinner" \N I say "I'm just getting it thinned by the hairdresser"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.36,0:13:56.60,Hosei,,0,0,0,,So maybe that was aired
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.16,0:14:01.96,Hosei,,0,0,0,,And Nukumizu-san saw that it seems
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:05.96,Hosei,,0,0,0,,He asked like "You're getting it thinned?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:08.40,Hamada,,0,0,0,,That's fine though
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:09.04,Endo,,0,0,0,,Why did he get mad
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.04,0:14:11.20,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You met him in the washroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:12.48,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Why does he care if you're getting it thinned
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.48,0:14:18.28,Hosei,,0,0,0,,"You're getting it thinned you say?" Is what he said
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.28,0:14:26.28,Hosei,,0,0,0,,And I said like "Oh, did I say that?" \N He replied "Yes you did"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:28.60,Hosei,,0,0,0,,"Hey asshole!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:30.48,Endo,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:30.76,Hosei,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:33.92,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Why though? What's there to get mad about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.92,0:14:38.04,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Maybe he was angry from the start
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:41.32,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,And it's not like you said anything to Nukumizu-san
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.32,0:14:45.32,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Yes exactly. In the start I had no idea what he was talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:53.32,Hosei,,0,0,0,,"By saying you're getting it thinned...Isn't your hair super thin?" he said
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:58.04,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Sorry I don't understand, I really don't understand
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.64,0:15:00.08,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Can I eat a mandarin please
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:02.64,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,No way, you're telling a story right now
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.20,0:15:05.60,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Yeah sorry I don't understand
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.24,0:15:06.52,Hosei,,0,0,0,,I can't eat a mandarin in the middle of my story
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.52,0:15:08.76,Endo,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:08.96,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.12,0:15:11.56,Endo,,0,0,0,,Nukumizu-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.56,0:15:14.36,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I can't understand at all. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.36,0:15:21.20,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Nukumizu-san, even though we've never met he really took care of me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:25.68,Endo,,0,0,0,,Nukumizu-san took care of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:30.28,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,So he got angry after that? I heard you got smacked
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:32.04,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Yes, it starts from here
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.04,0:15:38.48,Hosei,,0,0,0,,After that, so many times (nanpatsu)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:42.88,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Nanptsu sounds like Sanpatsu (haircut), so confusing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:48.72,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Enough already
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.16,0:15:54.20,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Enough already! Such a goddamn uninteresting story
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.52,0:15:57.84,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.84,0:15:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Endo nominates someone to tell a lie
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.88,0:16:00.60,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Endo-san
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.32,0:16:04.60,Endo,,0,0,0,,This is something that shocked all my juniors,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.60,0:16:08.16,Endo,,0,0,0,,Hamada-san, you've used a meridian channel before?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:09.08,Endo,,0,0,0,,When you press it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.08,0:16:10.92,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah I know that one
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.92,0:16:12.12,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,It makes you explode right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.12,0:16:14.84,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:14.96,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Ahhh yeah yes
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.96,0:16:17.48,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,But doesn't using it kill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.28,0:16:18.48,Endo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(686,901)}Yeah I wanted to know how you stopped it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.48,0:16:22.20,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah it's not a big deal, I just put some pressure on it
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:25.44,Endo,,0,0,0,,Oh, so it does make you swell?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.12,0:16:28.16,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Who made you explode?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:30.60,Endo,,0,0,0,,Was there a meridian channel master nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.24,0:16:30.76,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Yes yes
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:33.04,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I don't know exactly, but he went like "Hey Hey"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:35.08,Endo,,0,0,0,,Where did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.08,0:16:35.32,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,A foreigner?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:36.76,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Hey Hey?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:39.82,Hosei,,0,0,0,,\N{\rHamada}Like "here & here & here"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.82,0:16:45.60,Endo,,0,0,0,,Where did this happen? Were you eating, were you backstage?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:51.76,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It was on my way home. Right as I parked the car in the parking lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:54.24,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Wow so they totally ambushed you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:55.72,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I think I was being targeted
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.72,0:16:57.00,Hosei,,0,0,0,,You never saw them before?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:16:57.92,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Not at all
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.92,0:17:00.96,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,So it was like Fist of the North Star?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.96,0:17:04.68,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I don't know if it was like that, but he did have a Mohican haircut
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:08.42,Hosei,,0,0,0,,That's totally Zako from Fist of the North Star
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:11.60,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Wow, he really exists
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.16,0:17:17.44,Hamada,,0,0,0,,"What is this guy? What's his deal?" and slowly my face started swelling
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.84,0:17:19.96,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I went "Oh crap"!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.96,0:17:25.02,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Well it's a good thing you were in your neighborhood, you could go home right away
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:26.28,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Yes yes exactly. I was just swelling up like this
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.28,0:17:29.08,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I got home and said "Go get me some ice!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:33.32,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Oh right, you iced it down
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.48,0:17:36.24,Endo,,0,0,0,,So basically you just thought to put ice on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.24,0:17:39.72,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Yeah I didn't know what to do, I just thought ice is good for swelling
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.72,0:17:41.68,Hamada,,0,0,0,,And I gradually pushed it down
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.68,0:17:44.44,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,And nothing happened after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:49.28,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Like swelling up out of nowhere, or seeing some swelling when you wake up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.28,0:17:54.56,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Oh no, but actually like Endo just said, when I use the bath it does puff up a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.24,0:18:02.20,Hamada,,0,0,0,,I thought it would be bad to get a fever, so I just rushed out
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.20,0:18:04.04,Hamada,,0,0,0,,And I got the ice again
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.48,0:18:07.12,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Oh, you didn't mention that
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.60,0:18:15.28,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I would never have known without asking
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:16.32,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Tanaka-san
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:17.92,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Tanachi
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(728,856)}Tanaka nominates someone to tell a lie
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.64,0:18:24.60,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Well we were talking about Meridian Channels. And well I don't know if this is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.76,0:18:26.76,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Endo,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.76,0:18:30.72,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I heard you got bit by a zombie,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.72,0:18:35.16,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,and miraculously recovered to a human
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:38.80,Endo,,0,0,0,,Well whether or not I recovered is up to your judgment I guess,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:40.48,Endo,,0,0,0,,Have I recovered?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.48,0:18:45.76,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,I can't really tell, I thought that story was a lie
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.76,0:18:48.12,Endo,,0,0,0,,Then I think I have recovered. If I'm being serious
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:52.44,Endo,,0,0,0,,I do try to recover, but I can't really tell myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:57.00,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Isn't this turning out the same as Hamada's story?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:19:02.40,Endo,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, not at all, no no not at all
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.40,0:19:08.28,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,So it's true then, you got bit by a zombie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.44,0:19:11.20,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Zombies exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:13.48,Endo,,0,0,0,,Yes they exist, I got bit after all
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.48,0:19:14.64,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Where was this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.64,0:19:17.58,Endo,,0,0,0,,Right as I parked the car in the parking lot
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:18.56,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Parking lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.56,0:19:22.04,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Just like how I parked my car...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.28,0:19:26.40,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Well it was a different location of course
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:30.84,Endo,,0,0,0,,In a parking lot, he came out from behind the back of an Alphard
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.84,0:19:34.20,Endo,,0,0,0,,It just rushed me like *PAPAPAPA*, seriously just rushed me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.20,0:19:35.52,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,They move that fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:36.92,Endo,,0,0,0,,Yeah super fast
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.92,0:19:39.12,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Why though?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:44.08,Endo,,0,0,0,,Yeah like, like this he came at me, and bit me like,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.08,0:19:48.24,Endo,,0,0,0,,Here, this area, he bit me like this
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.64,0:19:51.48,Endo,,0,0,0,,Ow ow ow! I did that of course
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:57.08,Endo,,0,0,0,,It was pretty late at night, like 11:30, around then. He had his knife stabbed and his eye dangling
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.08,0:20:00.22,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Enough of that, what happened when it bit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:02.79,Endo,,0,0,0,,I went "OW!" and I thought for now I should,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.79,0:20:07.68,Endo,,0,0,0,,I should go home, and I told my wife "Let's try cooling it down"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:10.04,Hosei,,0,0,0,,With what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.04,0:20:12.64,Endo,,0,0,0,,Ice, from the refrigerator
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.64,0:20:15.44,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:17.64,Hosei,,0,0,0,,What were you even talking about at the end
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.04,0:20:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamada nominates someone to tell a lie
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:25.16,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Dahama-san
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.04,0:20:25.60,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Oh me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.60,0:20:30.44,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto-san, is it true, you've been asking the agency for some advice
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.44,0:20:31.68,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Oh, you know about it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.68,0:20:33.40,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Oh, is it about that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:35.04,Hosei,,0,0,0,,What thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.04,0:20:38.84,Hamada,,0,0,0,,He said something about turning his right hand into a drill
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:42.52,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Eh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:44.36,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,This is,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.36,0:20:47.88,Hamada,,0,0,0,,"Is it alright? Will the agency mind?" is what he's been asking I've heard
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:50.28,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Why do you wanna do it? The drill?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.28,0:20:55.60,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I was drinking with Takasu-sensei coincidentally,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:59.68,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,And he said something like "Don't turn it into a drill"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:03.42,Hosei,,0,0,0,,But why did he say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.56,0:21:03.72,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What's the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:08.04,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I was super conflicted but we decided on changing just 2 things
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.04,0:21:10.08,Hamada,,0,0,0,,That was fast, but why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:11.68,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Why a drill?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.68,0:21:15.76,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Why a drill? Alright listen I'm a southpaw,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.76,0:21:20.16,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,When I write I use my left hand, basically I do everything with my left hand
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.16,0:21:23.28,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,So thinking about how little I use my right hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.28,0:21:27.84,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,And when I talked about this to Takasu-sensei, he said like \N "Matsumoto-san, are you using righty?"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.84,0:21:30.12,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,And it just shocked me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:31.92,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,He said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.00,0:21:35.24,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It just convinced me, I thought let's do it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:38.04,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I've already got the mold made
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.92,0:21:41.84,Hamada,,0,0,0,,But, what's the point of the drill?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.84,0:21:43.60,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,Yeah, instead of a hand
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.60,0:21:48.68,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Even this, this is a fake hand
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.68,0:21:50.68,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's like a false tooth?\N{\rMatsumoto}It's like a false tooth
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.36,0:21:52.72,Hosei,,0,0,0,,It can work like a drill?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.72,0:21:55.88,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,No no, it's a temporary hand
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.88,0:21:58.12,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,They cut it off once,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.60,0:22:03.40,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,And when they attached it, it was rotating like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.40,0:22:07.12,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I asked, "Sensei, isn't this rotation weird?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:12.68,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,He said "Sorry!" it's a matter of millimeters after all,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.68,0:22:19.20,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,They got rid of the hand they cut off, so I have a temporary hand right now and it's kind of hard to move
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.20,0:22:20.44,Hosei,,0,0,0,,But I can't tell at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.44,0:22:22.02,Hamada,,0,0,0,,You were fine up until now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.76,0:22:26.80,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's something that I have to be aware of
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.80,0:22:29.28,Hamada,,0,0,0,,When do you rotate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.28,0:22:33.32,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Oh, like when I have a bad morning
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.16,0:22:35.64,Hosei,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.64,0:22:38.44,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I can massage myself like this when I have a bad morning
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.44,0:22:40.08,Hosei,,0,0,0,,Isn't that dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.16,0:22:42.40,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I don't do it that hard, it's my own drill after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.40,0:22:45.04,Endo,,0,0,0,,But isn't it dangerous when just wake up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.16,0:22:47.76,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yeah I could take some skin off, that's not good
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.48,0:22:52.36,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I just go "whir whir, whir whir" like this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.12,0:22:57.84,Hamada,,0,0,0,,If you're gonna bother doing that, you may as well wake up normally
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.20,0:23:01.72,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,It's not just for that, I can use it for cooking, and there's lots of attachments
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.28,0:23:04.72,Tanaka,,0,0,0,,It's not just a drill?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.72,0:23:08.60,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's also a thread spool one
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.60,0:23:10.04,Hamada,,0,0,0,,A thread spool?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.04,0:23:12.32,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Something to spool up the thread
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.80,0:23:18.80,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,And also, a thing for whipping stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.60,0:23:15.24,Endo,,0,0,0,,Do you use that though?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.32,0:23:21.44,Endo,,0,0,0,,But you don't cook that often though
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.44,0:23:26.00,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yeah the doctor laughed like "Now you can cook Matsumoto!" "GAHAHA"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.00,0:23:29.32,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That was the master at the bar laughing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.60,0:23:31.32,Endo,,0,0,0,,Oh right, the master
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.68,0:23:33.96,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,The master was listening on us the whole time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.52,0:23:39.40,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,And this is an inappropriate thing to say, but I can use it for {\i1}that{\i0} sort of thing too
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.52,0:23:40.60,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.60,0:23:44.52,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the drill, if I put something on the tip of it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.12,0:23:51.20,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I can use just the drill too though, like using the tip to *chin chin chin chin*
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.04,0:24:00.12,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,You know, I was forced to lie,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.12,0:24:03.76,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,And when I get a little dirty, you guys egg me on,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.76,0:24:09.08,Hamada,,0,0,0,,No no no, you could've ended the story earlier
